  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/535eb3c8423e71ac04d4d47d8bc0af8e.avif?t=1766537545\" width=452 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/125c0f735bf659533109df9f10df5cff.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/73edbb0681e626f79bf3c7d02407afbf.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/3a710e24305f1c2627f354da86537ff6.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/d36e2d9aed7ab1d600fda2cc6c16c731.avif?t=1766537545\" width=429 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cacildes Adventure</strong> is an Action RPG built around precise, skill-based combat and rewarding exploration in a handcrafted fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the king's army as a new recruit and find yourself caught between warring factions. Travel from the windswept forests of Slepbone to the bustling streets of Cecily Town, through shadowy dungeons and elvish settlements, as you confront the escalating conflict between orcs and elves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will determine which side claims victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.poster.avif?t=1766537545\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.webm?t=1766537545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.mp4?t=1766537545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A World of Challenge and Discovery</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master precise combat </strong>— dodges, parries, guard counters, jump attacks, backstabs, and magical abilities make every fight a test of timing and strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join forces - </strong>invite your brother to help you on your journey, or forge alliances with a demon prince who will descend into Hell itself by your side.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face deadly foes and unique threats</strong>, like the undead skeleton that rises every night to haunt the local church.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test yourself in combat arenas</strong> spread across the world, where waves of enemies push your mastery to the limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and upgrade a vast arsenal of weapons and spells</strong>, from ultraswords, scythes, and bows to elemental fireballs, lightning magic, and necromantic powers — all upgradeable at the forge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape your character and your story</strong>: allocate stats, choose your appearance, rename Cacildes, and define your legacy through your actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corner of Slepbone offers <strong>hidden paths, branching choices, and challenges that respond to your decisions</strong>. Fight, explore, craft, and survive — the world is yours to conquer, but nothing will be handed to you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/535eb3c8423e71ac04d4d47d8bc0af8e.avif?t=1766537545\" width=452 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/125c0f735bf659533109df9f10df5cff.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/73edbb0681e626f79bf3c7d02407afbf.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/3a710e24305f1c2627f354da86537ff6.avif?t=1766537545\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/d36e2d9aed7ab1d600fda2cc6c16c731.avif?t=1766537545\" width=429 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cacildes Adventure</strong> is an Action RPG built around precise, skill-based combat and rewarding exploration in a handcrafted fantasy world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the king's army as a new recruit and find yourself caught between warring factions. Travel from the windswept forests of Slepbone to the bustling streets of Cecily Town, through shadowy dungeons and elvish settlements, as you confront the escalating conflict between orcs and elves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will determine which side claims victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.poster.avif?t=1766537545\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.webm?t=1766537545\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2617740/extras/b77147b1b3caf75cbb3edf63c1a09bf2.mp4?t=1766537545\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A World of Challenge and Discovery</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master precise combat </strong>— dodges, parries, guard counters, jump attacks, backstabs, and magical abilities make every fight a test of timing and strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join forces - </strong>invite your brother to help you on your journey, or forge alliances with a demon prince who will descend into Hell itself by your side.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face deadly foes and unique threats</strong>, like the undead skeleton that rises every night to haunt the local church.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test yourself in combat arenas</strong> spread across the world, where waves of enemies push your mastery to the limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and upgrade a vast arsenal of weapons and spells</strong>, from ultraswords, scythes, and bows to elemental fireballs, lightning magic, and necromantic powers — all upgradeable at the forge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape your character and your story</strong>: allocate stats, choose your appearance, rename Cacildes, and define your legacy through your actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corner of Slepbone offers <strong>hidden paths, branching choices, and challenges that respond to your decisions</strong>. Fight, explore, craft, and survive — the world is yours to conquer, but nothing will be handed to you.</p>",
